data.description: The perfect single story waiting for a family to call home. This home in a quite part of Antioch with private backyard overlooking a beautiful park with lush landscape and trails for walking, large patio area and plenty of grass, newly installed hard wood floors, freshly painted interior, Side yard access and even a shed. The interior has a large living dining area that is spacious and open. Enjoy the kitchen/family room combo with a warm fireplace. There are 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms plus a spacious bonus room.
